The Cybersecurity Bootcamp at 4Geeks Academy is designed to help individuals become cybersecurity specialists, even without any prior knowledge in the field. The program covers a wide range of topics including Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. Students will also learn about risk management, data loss prevention strategies, and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. The bootcamp lasts for 16 weeks and includes 3 live online classes per week. Class sizes are limited to 16 people. Upon completion, students will receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. The median annual salary for cybersecurity professionals in the United States is $103,560. For more information, visit the [4Geeks Academy website](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop